    }
  }
}
```

### 4. Accessibility
- Use emoji sparingly (not everyone's terminal supports them)
- Provide text alternatives for visual elements
- Don't rely solely on color (use symbols too: âœ… âŒ âš ï¸)

### 5. Performance
- Don't call gum for every line in a loop
- Batch formatting when possible
- Use plain text for high-volume output

